Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據真實故事改編\NBased on a true story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托馬斯勳爵\NLord Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利勳爵\NLord Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安布羅斯勳爵\NLord Ambrose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅伯特勳爵\NLord Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾特勳爵\NLord Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好別令我失望 查爾斯·格雷\NYou'd better not let me down, Charles Grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在你身上投了20幾尼的賭注呢\NI've got 20 guineas riding on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才20?如果我是你 就會下雙倍\NOnly 20? I'd double that if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 女士們\NCome on, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾索普莊園 1774年四月\NAlthorp Estate England, April 1774
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 繞著跑道跑兩圈 聽我發令\NGentlemen, twice around the course, on my count.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三 二\NThree, two,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一!\None!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 格雷先生!      快點 托馬斯!\NCome on, Mr. Grey!        Come on, Thomas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 格雷先生!      跑起來 沃爾特勳爵\NCome on, Mr. Grey!        Run, Lord Walter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 格雷先生!\NCome on, Mr. Grey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 格雷先生!你不會是累了吧\NCome on, Mr. Grey. You're tired already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 格雷先生!      快點!\NCome on, Mr. Grey!        Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵您一定覺得喬治亞娜很有魅力吧?\NI trust Your Grace still finds Georgiana an attractive girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 斯賓塞夫人\NOf course, Lady Spencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是有教養的淑女\NShe's an accomplished lady of quality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恪盡職守\Nand devoted to her duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能說流利的法語 意大利語 拉丁語\NShe's fluent in French, Italian, Latin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精通騎術和舞蹈 還有...\Nand fully versed in horsemanship and dancing and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我看得出來 她是你的驕傲\NYes, I'm aware of all that. She's a credit to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不出任何理由阻礙\NI can't think of anything that would stand in the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,締結如此美滿快樂的婚姻\Nof a singularly happy marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些事情並不是公爵所擔心的 斯賓塞夫人\NThese are not the issues that burden the Duke, Lady Spencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵所考慮的是繼承人的問題\NIt is His Grace's duty to produce an heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換而言之 當那一天到來的時候\NOn the other hand, your daughter may expect
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的女兒必定有可觀的回報\Na handsome reward when that occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 希頓      不用客氣\NThank you, Heaton.        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵您大可以放心\NYour Grace may rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:02:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們家族的女人\NThe women in our family
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從未沒喪失過那方面的能力\Nhave never forfeited on that account.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然有此保證...\NWell, with that assurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣吧\NSo be it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 格雷先生!\NCome on, Mr. Grey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 女士們 但看來我的馬贏了\NI do apologize, ladies, but it appears that my horse has won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又擊敗我了 查爾斯\NBeat me again, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好 格雷先生      表現不錯\NWell done, Mr. Grey.        Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們欠你多少呢?      你欠我40\NSo how much do we owe you?        You owe me 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 40      我的報酬呢?\NTwenty, 40.        My reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什麼?\NAnd what do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您母親想見你 喬治亞娜小姐\NYour mother wishes to see you, Lady Georgiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 母親 我們是不是太吵鬧了?\NI must apologize, Mama. Were we making too much noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 親愛的\NNot at all, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有更重要的事要談 過來\NWe have more important things to talk of. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到有傳聞      什麼?\NI have heard a rumor.        Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說再過不久 我的女兒\NThat I will soon be addressing my daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能成為德文郡的公爵夫人\Nas Her Grace, the Duchess of Devonshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎 母親?      是的\NIs it true, Mama?        It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德文郡的公爵夫人?\NThe Duke of Devonshire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本想至少把你留到18歲\NI had hoped not to part with you until 18 at the soonest,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有此良緣\Nbut, with such a fine match,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不放你走就顯得我太自私了\Nit would be selfish of me not to let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他愛我?      是的 當然\NHe loves me?        Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只見過他兩次\NI have only met him twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當真心愛著一個人的時候\NWhen one truly loves someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不需要相交很深就能確定 喬治亞娜\None doesn't have to know them well to be sure, Georgiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能感受到\NOne feels it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你和他一起會很快樂\NI do believe you will be happy with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的 母親 我知道我會的\NI shall, Mama. I know I shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點!      她來了!\NCome on!        She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵夫人!公爵夫人!\NYour Grace! Your Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她來了!      公爵夫人!\NThere she is!        Duchess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想要什麼?\NWhat do they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是想見見我和我的新婚妻子\NTo see me and my new wife, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有點煩人 但你會習慣的\NIt can be a nuisance, but you'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倫敦 德文郡莊園\NDevonshire House,London
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您 公爵夫人\NWelcome, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 小傢伙 雨果 雨果 來\NCome, boys. Come on. Hugo, Hugo. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就這樣\NYes, yes, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:09:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 乖 乖 這邊走\NIt's all right. Yes, yes. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨果 來 小傢伙 過來\NHugo. Come, boy. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀 你們可以退下了\NScissors. You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何也想不明白\NFor the life of me, I could never understand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼女人的衣服要做得這麼複雜\Nwhy women's clothes must be so damn complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想這只是我們表現自己的方式而已\NIt's just our way of expressing ourselves, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是什麼?\NWhatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噯 你有這麼多方式表現自己\NWell, you have so many ways of expressing yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我們只能擺弄我們的帽子和裙子\Nwhereas we must make do with our hats and our dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上床來好嗎?\NWould you go to the bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人必須承擔自己的責任\NOne has to accept one's responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨結婚而來的義務\NCertain obligations come with marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管它們有多艱難\Nno matter how burdensome they may seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但我們在一起的時候...\NYes, but when we are together...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 當我們私下在一起的時候...\NBut when we are together, intimately, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 那的確很煩人\NI know. It can be a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要你能給他生個兒子\NHowever, it is only until you have given him a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的情況會減少 也不會那麼堅決\NThen the occasions will become fewer and less determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得只要他能不時跟我談談\NI think it might feel different
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就會很不一樣\Nif he would talk to me every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他並非不和藹 但他從來不和我交談\NI mean, it's not that he's unkind, but he never talks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為他就像父親那樣\NI thought that he would be like Papa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在冷酷的外表下\Nthat under his cool reserve
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著深沉的情感\Nthere'd be a wealth of depth and sentiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但除了他的狗 他對任何事情都不感興趣\Nbut he isn't interested in anything, apart from his dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬 試著別對他太苛求\NTry not to be too hard on His Grace, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只不過在履行責任而已\NHe's merely intent on fulfilling his duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於和他交談\NAnd as for talking to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可以談論的呢?\Nwell, whatever is there to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你說得對\NNo, you're quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然覺得自己能和丈夫交談\NHow foolish of me to think that I should be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太愚蠢了\Nconverse with my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治亞娜\NGeorgiana,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用耐心 堅毅和順從裝備自己\Nequip yourself with patience, fortitude and resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兒子很快就會降生 到時你就會知道了\NA boy will come soon enough, and then you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們 輝格黨\NBut we, the Whig Party,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:14:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僅將這視作公平 正義及明智\Nsimply see this as just, right and sensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將獨立帶給美洲\NJust to bring independence to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爭取廢除奴隸買賣\NRight to abolish the slave trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將自由帶給平民\NAnd sensible to bring freedom to the common man,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這片受到賜福的土地 這個英國\Nso the blessings of this blessed plot, this England,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將會賜福居於此處的居民 令他們享有更多平等\Nmay be more equally enjoyed by all of its inhabitants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要向我們的主人及恩人\NI would like to propose a toast to our host and benefactor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵及其美麗的公爵夫人敬酒\NHis Grace the Duke and his beautiful new Duchess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請起立\NPlease be upstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬公爵與公爵夫人!      敬公爵與公爵夫人！\NThe Duke and Duchess!        The Duke and Duchess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是出色的演講啊 福克斯先生\NExcellent speech, Mr. Fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙誇獎\NI thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向一群朋友演講總是比較容易的\NIt is always easier to address a congregation of friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其當那些朋友喝醉的時候\Nparticularly when those friends are drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵夫人對福克斯先生的演講有何看法呢?\NAnd how did the Duchess find Mr. Fox's speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得承認 政治演講令我感到不太自在\NI must confess, I am not yet at ease with political speeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的形式妨礙我\NTheir very form tends to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看出他們的真正含義\Nobstruct my view of their actual meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如若真有含義的話\Nif such there be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演說的哪一部分\NIn which particular section of the speech
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令你難以理解呢 夫人?\Ndid the message elude Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同情你對大眾的感情\NWell, I have great sympathy with your sentiments in general,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我並不理解我們\Nbut I fail to fully comprehend how far we,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是輝格黨\Nthe Whig Party, that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離堅定實現自由有多遠\Nare fully committed to the concept of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想要擴大投票範圍      面向所有人?\NWe intend to extend the vote.        To all men?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天吶 當然不是\NHeavens, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定是面向更多人 適度自由\NBut certainly to more men. Freedom in moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"適度自由"?\N"Freedom in moderation"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是\NPrecisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你是出於好心 福克斯先生\NI'm sure you are full of the best intentions, Mr. Fox,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我敢肯定 假如我能投票的話\Nbut I dare say I would not spend my vote,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:16:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會把自己的一票浪費在這麼含糊的陳述上\Nif I had it, of course, on so vague a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個宣稱自由 另一個不是\NOne is either free or one is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而自由的概念是絕對的\NThe concept of freedom is an absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟人不能適度死亡\NAfter all, one cannot be moderately dead
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或適度被愛 又或適度自由\Nor moderately loved or moderately free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須二擇其一\NIt must always remain a matter of either or.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說幾句話\NI think it appropriate to say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當...\NWhen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能否看一下房間\NCould you check the chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看能不能找到      大人\Nand see if you can find...        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...別的法國緞帶?\N...different kinds of French lace?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎？      沒有\NIs anything the matter?        No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛離席了      是的 我已經吃完了\NYou just left.        Yes. Well, I had done eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而那些該死的演講令我煩心\Nand those damn speeches bore me to distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得以後應該禁止他們演講\NI think we have to ban them in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你是輝格黨的主要支持者\NBut you are the Whigs' main supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我並不反感政治\NYes. Well, I've no problem with the politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是無法忍受誇誇其談\NIt's just the rhetoric I can't stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該和你一起去嗎?\NShall I come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 為什麼要跟我一起去?\NNo. I mean, why ever should you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵大人很好 只是想休息一會而已\NThe Duke is perfectly well. He simply wanted to rest a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐 先生們\NDo sit down, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是演講太長令公爵難以忍受嗎?\NWas it the length of the speech that got the better of the Duke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是\NCertainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他非常喜歡\NHe enjoyed it immensely
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還希望下次能說得再長一點\Nand expressed a hope that next time it would be even longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬公爵夫人      敬福克斯先生\NYour Grace.        Mr. Fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?      你無需過問\NWhat's going on?        Nothing to concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白      過來\NI don't understand.        Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚很美 這裙子是你設計的?\NYou look very beautiful tonight. Is this dress your design?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 謝謝誇獎\NYes, it is. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你應當樂意讓你的丈夫\NThen I think you should allow your husband to appreciate it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欣賞更多細節\Nin a little more detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 叫他們進來      我們有客人嗎?\NYes, send them in.        Are we having company?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這羊肉嘗起來不太一樣嗎?\NDon't you think this mutton has a funny taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不會      我覺得是\NNo. Not really, no.        I think it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬 這位是夏洛特 她將和我們住在一起\NG, this is Charlotte, and she will be staying with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她母親去世了 她沒別的地方可去\NBecause her mother is dead, and she has no other place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是你的?\NHave you fathered that child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她...她不過是個小女孩 喬\NIt's... It's only a little girl, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是世界末日\NIt's hardly the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我來照顧她?\NAre you expecting me to look after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的房子有的是空房間\NWe have a house full of vacant rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不會麻煩你\NShe needn't bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上 她會對你很有用處\NIn fact, she may even be of use to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以練習為人母親的技巧\NYou can practice your mothering skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到我們的兒子出生為止\Nuntil our son arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 嘗起來不像正常的羊肉\NNo, this doesn't taste like normal mutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得裏面肯定加了點東西\NI'm sure there is something the matter with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿走好嗎?\NCould you take it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘗起來像正常羊肉嗎?\NDoes it taste like normal mutton?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘗起來像正常羊肉嗎?來\NDoes it taste like normal mutton? Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就當它是正常羊肉吧 挑食的小傢伙\NThink it tastes like normal mutton, fussy dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挑食的小狗狗\NWho's a fussy mutton dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的娃娃有名字嗎?\NDoes your doll have a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定很喜歡她的新睡房\Nl bet you she loves being in her new bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給她取個名字 明天告訴我好嗎\NYou'll have to think of a name and let me know tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能做到嗎?夏洛特\NDo you think you'll be able to do that, Charlotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...\Nl...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我們單獨呆一會 好嗎?      是 夫人\NWould you leave us, please?        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 夏洛特\NHello, Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫喬治亞娜\NMy name is Georgiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好      謝謝\NGood evening.        Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 夫人\NGood evening, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再大一英吋 夫人您就要分娩了\NAn inch more and I do believe Your Grace will explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝裏登一向深諳恭維之道\NSheridan always knows how to pay a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是得等上幾個星期\NStill a few more weeks to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰 挺著個大肚子都不會好看\NA huge belly has never been more becoming on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福克斯在說經驗之談呢\NWell, Fox, here, offers an expert opinion seeing,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次經過鏡子旁邊 他都能看到自己的大肚子\Nas he does, a giant belly every time he passes a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的大肚子是長在女人身上\NIf your belly were on a woman, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.36,0:23:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都知道是意味著什麼\Nwe'd all know what to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的謝裏登\NMy dear Sheridan,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個小時前 我的大肚子壓是在一個女人身上\Nan hour ago my belly was on a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.29,0:23:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你怎麼想?\NNow what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這教訓你在賭局開始前\NThat will teach you to insult Mr. Fox
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要侮辱福克斯先生\Nbefore the gaming has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.84,0:23:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\NIt's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止下注\NNo more bets, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人又贏了\NHer Grace wins again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.26,0:24:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再賭一把?\NAnother wager?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.57,0:24:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 夫人?      夫人!\NAre you all right, Your Grace?        Your Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.58,0:24:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是陣痛嗎?我的妻子要分娩了\NAre those labor pains? My wife is in labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.31,0:24:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點\NCome along.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.38,0:24:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想這值得敬酒\NI think this calls for a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.82,0:24:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許我的繼承人會在夜晚過去前降生\NI may have an heir before the night is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.69,0:24:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們 敬第六代德文郡公爵\NLadies and gentlemen, I give you the sixth Duke of Devonshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.66,0:24:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第六代德文郡公爵!\NThe sixth Duke of Devonshire!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.49,0:25:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人\NYour Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.77,0:25:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在什麼都不想說\NI am in no mood for a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.36,0:25:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 請務必告訴我 我的女兒是否...\NBut, pray tell me, is my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.69,0:25:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的女兒是否能為我誕下麟兒?\NIs your daughter at all able to give me a son?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.50,0:25:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 大人\NTake heart, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.13,0:25:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要母親健康\NAs long as the mother is in good health,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.90,0:25:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這次不幸當作是草稿\Nconsider this mishap a draft,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.00,0:25:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即將降臨的諾言\Na promise of what is soon to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.97,0:25:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們的家族 我們...      是的 我知道 在你的家族裏\NIn our family, we...        Yes, I know, in your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.77,0:25:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的家族裏\Nin your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.61,0:25:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先告退\NYour Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.15,0:25:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到這光芒嗎?看到嗎?\NCan you see the light? Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.50,0:26:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 你怎麼樣了?      我很好\NDarling, how are you?        Quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.47,0:26:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是否健康強壯?      她很完美\NIs she strong and healthy?        She's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.01,0:26:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威廉接待了你嗎?      是的\NDid William receive you?        Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.48,0:26:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是否因她不是兒子而不高興?\NIs he upset that she's not a son?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.42,0:26:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看了她一眼就離開了\NHe just glanced at her and then left.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.96,0:26:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後我就很少見到他了\NI've hardly seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.89,0:26:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這段時期對公爵大人來說不好過 親愛的\NIt's been a difficult time for His Grace, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.99,0:26:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人在盯著他 而並非所有人都是友善的\NMany eyes are upon him and not all of them kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.83,0:26:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個美女\NShe is the loveliest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.34,0:26:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶媽?      不 我親自哺育她\NNurse?        No, I will feed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.87,0:26:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說真的嗎 親愛的?     是的\NAre you sure, darling?        Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.28,0:26:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我是她的母親 即使她是個女孩\NI am her mother, after all, even if she is only a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.35,0:26:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.02,0:27:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死的!\NHell and damnation!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.94,0:27:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6年後\NSix years later
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.42,0:27:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特(右)\NCharlotte
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.29,0:27:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏蘿(左)\NHarryo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.72,0:27:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小喬治亞娜(中)\NLittle G
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.03,0:27:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴斯\NThe City of Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.73,0:27:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外出度假以尋求智慧之言\NIt is always a pleasure when one is on holiday
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.97,0:27:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是令人愉快的\Nto request a few words of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.54,0:27:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不再贅言\NAnd so without further ado,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.24,0:27:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我榮幸地請出\Nit is a great honor to hand over to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.00,0:27:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們最高貴的來賓\Nour most distinguished guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.04,0:27:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當她出現 所有目光都凝注在她身上\NWhen she arrives, all eyes are upon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.18,0:28:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當她離開 她是人們談論的對象\NWhen absent, she is the subject of universal conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.32,0:28:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她今晚所穿之物\NAnd what we see her wearing tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.42,0:28:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我期望明天看到你們都穿上!\NI look forward to seeing the rest of you wearing tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.49,0:28:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有請時尚女王 德文郡公爵夫人\NThe empress of fashion herself, the Duchess of Devonshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.91,0:28:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來巴斯是想擺脫倫敦\NWe come away to Bath to get away from London,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.64,0:28:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到整個倫敦都來了巴斯\Nand all of London has come away to Bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.51,0:28:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確有人問過我\NSomebody did indeed ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.41,0:28:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我戴的是什麼羽毛\Nwhat kind of feather it is that I'm wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.02,0:28:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種稀有鳥類\NWell, there are only two specimens
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.90,0:28:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上只剩兩隻\Nof this rare bird known to man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.15,0:28:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一隻顯然在我頭上\NOne of them has clearly ended up on top of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.52,0:28:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而另一隻\NAnd the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.26,0:28:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據傳言是放在保守黨的辦公室裏\Nrumor has it, is running for office in the Tory Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.39,0:29:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲·福斯特\NBess Foster.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.83,0:29:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.77,0:30:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們尚未互相介紹吧\NI don't believe we've been introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.33,0:30:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是伊麗莎白·福斯特夫人\NNo, we haven't. Lady Elizabeth Foster.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.61,0:30:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你和我丈夫談話\NI saw you talking with my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.72,0:30:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他想跳舞\NYes. He wanted to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.47,0:30:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這通常不是他的長處 你婉謝了嗎?\NThat's not usually considered his forte. And you declined?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.59,0:30:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前我並不想要任何異性的陪伴\NI'm ill at ease with male company for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.99,0:30:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.33,0:30:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是什麼風把你吹來巴斯?\NSo what brings you to Bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.57,0:30:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的丈夫福斯特先生\NMy husband, Mr. Foster,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.29,0:30:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正和情婦在伯恩茅斯風流快活\Nis enjoying his mistress in Bournemouth
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.41,0:30:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想找點消遣 你呢?\Nand I wanted some diversion. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.68,0:30:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵是來浸浴治療痛風\NThe Duke is taking the waters for his gout.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.82,0:30:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我是為了自己的健康      真的?\NAnd I for my health.        Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.95,0:30:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你來這裏是因為生不出兒子\NI heard you were here because you could not conceive a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.46,0:30:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒 我不該說這樣的話\NI beg your pardon, that was an awful thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.89,0:31:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少說的是實話\NIt was the truth, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了愚蠢的話 我一直都這樣\NTrust me to say something silly. I always do, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.43,0:31:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也許你該接受公爵的邀請\NThen perhaps you should have accepted the Duke's offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.47,0:31:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們有很多共同點\NYou have much in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.41,0:31:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想該回家了 喬治亞娜\NHome, I think, Georgiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.79,0:31:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你住在哪裏呢?      我在鎮上租了幾個房間\NWhere are you staying?        I've rented some rooms in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.56,0:31:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要再見面      一定會的\NWe must meet again.        We must.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.88,0:31:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏蘿 過來 過來 疼嗎?\NHarryo. Come here. Come here. Did that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.92,0:32:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽      我的小天使\NMama.        My angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.42,0:32:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疼嗎?疼不疼?\NAre you sore? Was that sore?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.44,0:32:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看 是膝蓋嗎?\NLet me have a look. Was it this knee?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.13,0:32:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會沒事的\NI think you shall live.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.00,0:32:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 衝到橋上去 我數三聲 一 二 三 跑\NRight. First to the bridge on my count. One, two, three. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.60,0:32:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊 夏蘿\NCome on, Harryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.94,0:32:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我會追上她的      我會追上你的!\NNo, I'm gonna catch her!        I'm gonna catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.21,0:32:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跌倒了再爬起來\NUp and down. Up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.71,0:32:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們不能像那樣重新開始呢?\NWhy can't we recover like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.51,0:32:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已長大成人了\NIt's too far to fall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.58,0:32:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又見面了 你好      你好 你的女兒很漂亮\NHello again.        Hello. Your girls are lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.18,0:32:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 你有孩子嗎?      我有 三個男孩\NThank you. Do you have any children?        I do. Three boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.12,0:32:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三個男孩\NThree boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.03,0:32:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕能得到一個 公爵就已經願意捨棄一切了\NWhat the Duke wouldn't give for one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.63,0:32:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年紀最大的那個長得最不像你\NShe is least like you, your eldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.77,0:32:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我想你都聽說了吧\NYes. I'm sure you know the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.67,0:32:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們結婚之前 我丈夫的女兒已經出生\NMy husband's daughter was born before we married.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.14,0:33:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的母親是個女僕 女僕死後我們接收了那個孩子\NHer mother was a maid. The maid died, and we took the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.22,0:33:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我是不是說得太多了?      不是\NI'm sorry. Have I spoken out of turn?        No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.19,0:33:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這在倫敦已是公開的秘密了\NIt's the worst kept secret in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.55,0:33:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在已經九歲了\NShe's nine years old now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.99,0:33:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愛她?\NAnd you love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.82,0:33:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 就像自己親生的一樣\NOf course I do. The same as all my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.26,0:33:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來見見他們\NCome and meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.63,0:33:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘們 過來見見我的新朋友 伊麗莎白夫人\NGirls. Come and meet my new friend, Lady Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.11,0:33:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人      謝謝 溫泉水\NYour Grace.        Thank you. Thermal water.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.78,0:33:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那股味道是硫帶來的\NIt's the sulfur that makes it smell so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.78,0:33:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要喝這個嗎?\NAnd you really have to drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.03,0:33:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天兩次 喝一個月\NTwice a day for four weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.06,0:33:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道自己為什麼生不出男孩呢?\NDo you have any reason to believe you cannot birth a male?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.23,0:33:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 除了流產\NNo. Except miscarriages.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.00,0:33:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩次產下死胎 都是男胎\NTwo stillbirths, both sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.17,0:33:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但能生下兩個健康的女孩\NBut two healthy girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.25,0:34:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都在盯著你\NEverybody is staring at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.56,0:34:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你脖子上的是什麼?貝絲\NWhat's that on your neck? Bess?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.40,0:34:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用棍毆打妻子並不犯法\NIt's not illegal for a man to beat his wife with a stick
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.33,0:34:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非棍子比他的拇指還厚\Nunless the stick is thicker than his thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.44,0:34:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福斯特先生?但他不可能做這樣的事!\NMr. Foster? But he can't have done that!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.51,0:34:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想他對我做過的其他事\NWell, considering what else he's done to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.92,0:34:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這已經不是最糟的\Nthat's not the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.97,0:34:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼更糟的?\NWhat could possibly be worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.75,0:34:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他奪走我的孩子 不讓我見他們\NHe's taken my children. He won't let me see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.29,0:34:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦呢?\NAnd what do you propose to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.80,0:34:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的無計可施了\NReally, I'm at my wits' end.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.03,0:34:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法律站在福斯特先生那邊\NThe law supports Mr. Foster.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.80,0:35:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這段時間你住在哪裏呢?\NIn the meantime, where shall you stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.90,0:35:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續租住 直到錢用盡為止\NContinue lodging, till the money runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.78,0:35:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少這一點我能幫得上忙\NWell, there, at least, I think I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.95,0:35:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威廉?我們明天就離開\NWilliam? We leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.19,0:35:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊麗莎白夫人起碼有一段時間\NAnd Lady Elizabeth doesn't have to meet her parents
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.73,0:35:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要去內陸看父母\Non the continent for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.32,0:35:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她都沒怎麼參觀過倫敦呢\NShe hardly ever visits London at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.40,0:35:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾啊\NIt's a pity, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.54,0:35:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧 她沒別的地方可以呆了\NYou see, she doesn't have anywhere to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.38,0:35:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個問題\NProblem there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.52,0:35:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼她為什麼不和我們住在一起呢?\NWell, why doesn't she stay with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.12,0:35:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少呆上一段時間\NFor a while, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.39,0:35:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.30,0:36:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議啊      在愛爾蘭有城堡\NThis is incredible.        There's the castle in lreland.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.23,0:36:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博爾頓修道院 齊斯克之屋 百靈頓大屋\NBolton Abbey, Chiswick, Burlington and,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.37,0:36:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然還有察茲沃斯宮\Nwhy, in Chatsworth, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.70,0:36:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然      那更大了\NOf course.        Which is much bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.74,0:36:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這裏更像一個家\NBut this is more like home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.68,0:36:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興你在這裏\NI'm so glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.32,0:36:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為這個季度安排了一個精彩的起點\NI've arranged a wonderful start to the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.32,0:36:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我再和你做朋友\NMay all the plagues of marriage be doubled on me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.33,0:36:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我加倍承受婚姻的折磨吧\Nif ever I try to be friends with you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.63,0:36:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就更好了\NSo much the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.74,0:36:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 夫人 顯然你一點也不在乎我!\NNo, no, madam. 'Tis evident you care not a pin for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.24,0:36:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娶你這樣的人 我真是發瘋了\NAnd I, I was a madman to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.61,0:36:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嫁給你這樣的人 我真是蠢極了\NAnd I'm sure I was a fool to marry you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.05,0:37:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖欲跌的單身老漢\Nan old dangling bachelor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.29,0:37:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單身到五十歲\Nwho was single at 50
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.63,0:37:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只因從來沒有人看上他!\Nonly because he never could meet with anyone who could have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.42,0:37:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲 請容許我介紹福克斯先生 反對派的領袖\NBess, may I introduce Mr. Fox, leader of the Opposition?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.39,0:37:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福克斯先生 這位是伊麗莎白·福斯特夫人      福克斯先生\NMr. Fox, Lady Elizabeth Foster.        Mr. Fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.89,0:37:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的門生 查爾斯·格雷      格雷先生\NMy protege, Charles Grey.        Mr. Grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.10,0:37:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格雷先生      夫人\NMr. Grey.        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.83,0:37:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們的新進英才\NHe's our newest bright young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.37,0:37:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛從劍橋畢業不久 就已經位列議會\NScarcely out of Cambridge and already a member of Parliament.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.51,0:37:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得你很出色      謝謝\NI always felt you'd do well.        Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.44,0:37:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福克斯先生      伊麗莎白夫人\NMr. Fox.        Yes, Lady Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.68,0:38:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡這個戲劇嗎?\NDid you enjoy the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.14,0:38:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得老實承認 並不太喜歡\NI must confess, I did not entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.62,0:38:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你進入政界之後\NI hope that you've not lost your sense of humor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.59,0:38:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有喪失幽默感      我並不擔心這個\Nsince entering politics.        Not that I'm aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.26,0:38:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你想必意識到《造謠學校》（英國古典派喜劇）\NThen I'm sure you realize that School for Scandal
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.96,0:38:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是被當作喜劇來描寫      是的\Nwas written as a comedy.        Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.10,0:38:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管從我的角度看來 它更像是悲劇\NAlthough, from where I sat, it read as a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.20,0:38:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人!我們多想念你啊\NYour Grace! How we have missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.24,0:38:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺了你\NIn your absence,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.34,0:38:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倫敦變得沉悶不堪\NLondon has been reduced to the dreariest province.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.18,0:38:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是劇作家謝裏丹先生\NAnd this, of course, is the playwright Mr. Sheridan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.01,0:38:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請容許我介紹伊麗莎白·福斯特夫人\NMay I present the Lady Elizabeth Foster?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.41,0:38:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並非有意打擾\NI do not mean to be rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.65,0:38:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的所有演員都極想覲見公爵夫人\Nbut I've an entire cast dying to meet the Duchess.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.92,0:38:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一會就把你送回來 我保證\NI shall return you in a moment. Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.46,0:38:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福克斯先生?      嗯?\NMr. Fox?        Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.53,0:38:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借一步說話\NA word.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.66,0:38:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪裏發掘國內醜聞的題材呢?\NWell, wherever do I glean such domestic gossip?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.40,0:38:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對公爵大人公平嗎?\NWere we fair on the Duke?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.85,0:38:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來還可以更糟糕的\NIt could have been worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.60,0:38:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原定的劇名是《糟糕的婚姻》\NMy original title was The Bad Marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.27,0:39:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況真的是這樣的嗎?\NIs it always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.68,0:39:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噯 正如他們所說\NWell, as they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.58,0:39:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德文郡公爵是全英國唯一\Nthe Duke of Devonshire must be the only man in England
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.91,0:39:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愛慕他妻子的人\Nnot in love with his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.68,0:39:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是德文郡公爵夫人\NHer Grace, the Duchess of Devonshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.48,0:39:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很榮幸見到您\NVery pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.83,0:39:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已拋開那一切 玩得開心嗎?\NWere you at all able to forget things and enjoy yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.00,0:39:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是很好的娛樂 謝謝\NIt was a wonderful distraction, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.04,0:39:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.74,0:39:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一整晚都在和格雷先生交談      是嗎?\NI talked to Mr. Grey all evening.        Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.18,0:39:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他愛上你了\NHe's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.78,0:39:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的貝絲 不 他不是的 恐怕剛好相反\NMy dear Bess, no, he is not. Quite the reverse, I fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.95,0:39:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道感覺不到他凝視你的眼神嗎?\NWell, can't you tell by the way he looks at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.76,0:39:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說真的 你真的感覺不到嗎?      別說了\NHonestly, can't you tell?        Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.20,0:40:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治亞娜 交合併不只是為了後嗣\NGeorgiana, intercourse is not just about offspring.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.37,0:40:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上 是可以很愉悅的      我知道\NIn fact, it can be rather pleasurable.        Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.44,0:40:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛想像一下\NClose your eyes and try to envisage Grey
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.41,0:40:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格雷先生掀開你的裙子 親吻你的後背\Nopening your dress, kissing your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.65,0:40:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會做那樣的事      會的 他們會\NThey never do such things.        Yes, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.30,0:40:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上你的眼睛\NClose your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.44,0:40:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格雷在你背後慢慢的打開你的裙子\NGrey is behind you slowly opening your dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.24,0:40:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 貝絲 別說了!      閉上眼\NNo, Bess, stop!        Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.19,0:41:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻你的後背\NKissing your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.85,0:41:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.29,0:41:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧?\NSee?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.19,0:42:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下\NWould you excuse me for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.49,0:42:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人      格雷先生\NYour Grace.        Mr. Grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.03,0:42:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選舉在六星期後舉行 是吧?\NThe national election is in six weeks, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.76,0:42:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,競選進行得怎樣了?\NHow is the campaign going?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.67,0:42:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很糟糕\NTerribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.04,0:42:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們唯一的希望的是為福克斯保住威斯敏斯特\NOur only hope is to save Westminster for Fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.64,0:42:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所知 我有很多毛病\NI have many faults, as you well know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.98,0:42:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中包括善於吸引別人的目光\NNot least among them is my ability to draw attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.75,0:42:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們可以利用那點作為我們的優勢\NPerhaps we could use that to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.67,0:42:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們\NLadies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.17,0:42:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們\NLadies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.27,0:43:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你們介紹 指引我們該做何事\NI give you the man who will inform us of the work we must do
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.04,0:43:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該信何黨派的人 查爾斯·格雷先生\Nand of the party we so believe in. Mr. Charles Grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.65,0:43:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威斯敏斯特的人們!\NGood people of Westminster!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.12,0:43:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界正面臨崩潰或得救的邊緣\NThe world is on the brink of disaster or salvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.53,0:43:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從法國到美洲\NFrom France to America,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.30,0:43:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人和女人都在為自己的自由而奮鬥\Nmen and women are struggling to free themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.40,0:43:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找自我存在的價值!\Nto find meaning in their existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.91,0:43:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革就在我們眼前!\NChange is upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.88,0:43:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不應倒退回舊日\NWe shall not go back to the old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.68,0:43:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應當把英國帶進勇敢的新時代\NWe shall take England into this brave new world
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.95,0:43:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撼動天空!\Nand shake the thunder from the skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.80,0:44:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我表現得怎樣?      我覺得你並不困窘\NHow did I do?        I think it was not an embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.04,0:44:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇跡\NIt was a marvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.38,0:44:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很緊張 你的到場令我的緊張放大了三倍\NI was nervous. Your presence trebled the numbers at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.38,0:44:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使現在 我仍然緊張\NI'm nervous even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.00,0:44:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如我能贏得選舉 假如我得到權力\NIf we win this election, if we get the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.33,0:44:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想我們能做什麼\Nthink what we will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.39,0:44:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們分開的時候 你有想我嗎?\NDo you think of me when we're not together?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.40,0:44:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我有的\NYou ought to know I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.00,0:44:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在回答之前 你猶豫了      不\NYou hesitated before you replied.        No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.45,0:44:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒有人這麼直接問我\NI'm unused to being asked so directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.49,0:44:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是你還是其他人\NAnd by you, of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.63,0:45:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想著你 無時無刻都想\NI think of you all the time. I always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.74,0:45:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的馬車在等著呢 夫人      謝謝\NYour carriage awaits, Your Grace.        Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.67,0:45:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...我們就此立誓\N...this we vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.40,0:45:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在伊麗莎白夫人的房間外面做什麼?\NWhat are you doing outside Lady Elizabeth's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.95,0:45:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰和她在裏面?\NWho's in there with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.18,0:47:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英國有那麼多女人 你偏偏要纏上她\NOf all the women in England you had to throw yourself on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.39,0:47:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從未拒絕過你任何事\NI have never once objected to any of your affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.23,0:47:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接受所有你作出的安排\NI have accepted whatever arrangement you have proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.94,0:47:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將夏洛特視為己出\NI have raised Charlotte as my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.64,0:47:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這個...\NBut this...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.11,0:47:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我唯一僅剩的\NI have one single thing of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.49,0:47:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不能把伊麗莎白留給我?\NWhy couldn't you let me keep Elizabeth for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.09,0:47:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人啊?\NWhat kind of man are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.87,0:47:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們的婚姻生活裏 她是唯一能給我慰藉的\NShe is my sole comfort in our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.85,0:48:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搶走了我唯一的朋友!\NYou have robbed me of my only friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.05,0:48:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我犯了什麼錯?\NWhat is wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.31,0:48:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...\Nl...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.41,0:48:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說過我是感性的人 喬\NI've never claimed to be a man of fine sensibility, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.88,0:48:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我很清楚自己想從這段婚姻中得到什麼\NBut I've always known what I expect from this marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.25,0:48:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和付出什麼\Nand what I'm prepared to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.76,0:48:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為丈夫 我履行了自己的義務\NAs a husband, I have fulfilled my obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.86,0:49:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但作為妻子\NBut, as a wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.50,0:49:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有\Nyou have not.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.74,0:49:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要離開 馬上就走\NShe has to go. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.24,0:49:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能踏入這房子半步!\NShe is never to set foot in this house again!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.94,0:49:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬 控制一下自己的脾氣 你太失禮了\NDo mind your temper, G. You're forgetting yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.35,0:49:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要她走\NI want her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.12,0:49:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想見到她\NI never want to lay eyes on her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.05,0:49:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下去叫她馬上走\NGo down and tell her to leave at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.46,0:49:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能要她那麼做\NI couldn't ask her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.06,0:49:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會那樣做 喬\NI won't do it, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.98,0:49:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始我就不喜歡她\NI never liked her from the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.85,0:49:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得很清楚了 母親\NYou made that quite clear, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.29,0:50:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願她已經離開了德文郡莊園\NShe's gone from Devonshire House, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.09,0:50:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們一起住在那裏?\NThey're living there together?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.20,0:50:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治亞娜!你居然容忍這樣的事?\NGeorgiana! What have you permitted to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.63,0:50:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 我不知道\NI don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.37,0:50:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我 幫幫我 求你了 母親 告訴我該怎麼辦\NHelp me. Help me, please, Mama. Tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.58,0:50:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得寫信給丈夫 堅持要求送走她\NYou must write to your husband and insist he send her back
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.78,0:50:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回她原來呆的糟糕地方\Nto whatever horrid little place she came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.05,0:50:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不會的 他說"這是不可能的"\NHe will not. ''It is out of the question,'' he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.56,0:50:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你要回去 履行為人妻子的義務\NThen you must return and resume your duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.50,0:50:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她知道他真正愛的人是誰\NMake him realize whom he loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.13,0:50:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要放棄政治生活和賭博\NYou will give up your politics and your gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.00,0:50:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次 你要全心全意做個好妻子\NFor once, you will devote yourself as a loving wife
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.41,0:50:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親手解決問題 給他生一個繼承人\Nand settle down to the task in hand, providing him with an heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.78,0:51:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼他很快就會厭倦她\NThen he will soon tire of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.82,0:51:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有其他選擇\NYou have no other option.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.76,0:51:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 喬\NHello, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.33,0:51:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威廉\NWilliam.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.00,0:52:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也許無權將你趕出房子\NI may not have the authority to remove you from my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.11,0:52:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我至少可以命令你離開我的房間\Nbut I can, at least, order you out of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.84,0:52:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能聽我解釋嗎?\NWon't you please let me explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.81,0:52:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好解釋的\NThere is nothing to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.98,0:52:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我見孩子們的唯一機會\NThis is my only chance of ever seeing my children again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.75,0:52:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵是英國最有權勢的貴族\NThe Duke is the most powerful peer in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.06,0:52:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我唯一的機會\NHe is my only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.39,0:52:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是為了孩子 犧牲也是有個限度的\NThere are limits to the sacrifices one makes for one's children.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.43,0:52:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的 犧牲一切也不為過\NNo, there aren't. No limits whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.67,0:53:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去\NGet out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.84,0:53:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間沒什麼好說的\NWe have nothing more to say to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.73,0:54:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽\NMama, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.47,0:54:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見到你真好 媽媽\NIt's so nice to see you, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.14,0:54:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這是獵槍\NRight, this is a shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.81,0:54:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你母親說你會感興趣的 對嗎?\NYour mother said you'd be interested, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.84,0:54:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.48,0:54:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是打火石 你看到了嗎?\NThis is a flint. Do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.28,0:54:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當打火石撞到這裏 就會產生火花\NWhen the flint hits there, it causes a spark to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.42,0:54:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火花點燃火藥\NNow, the spark, it lights the gunpowder
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.71,0:54:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把子彈推出槍外\Nand sends the bullet out of the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.39,0:54:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道怎麼拿槍嗎?      不知道 先生\NDo you know how to hold it?        No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.63,0:54:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的\NWell, it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.14,0:54:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夾在右邊腋窩下\NTuck it in there,into your right shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.29,0:54:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊的托住\NHold it firmly,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.26,0:54:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隻手可以再挪遠一點\Nthen you can move that hand a little further along.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.90,0:54:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你感受到它的重量了吧?要再往前傾一點\NCan you feel how heavy it is? You have to lean into it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.04,0:54:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻眼睛保持睜開 順著槍管看過去\NAnd keep both eyes open. Look right along the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.11,0:54:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣\NRight along there just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.45,0:54:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砰!來 我做給你看看\NBang! Here, let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.06,0:55:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.29,0:55:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很沉 是吧?\NIt's quite heavy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.76,0:55:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你口渴嗎?要不要喝點什麼?\NAre you thirsty? Would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.87,0:55:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們口渴嗎?要喝點什麼嗎?\NAre you gentlemen thirsty? Would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.64,0:55:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.79,0:56:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有告訴公爵要見什麼人呢?\NDid you tell the Duke who you were meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.03,0:56:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.93,0:56:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他問了嗎?      沒有\NDid he even ask?        No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.00,0:56:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還有別的事情要想\NHe has other things on his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.87,0:56:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣\NAs do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.71,0:56:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是說出來會不會好一點?\NWould it help to unburden yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.95,0:56:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能跟你討論那些事\NIt's nothing I can discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.35,0:56:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算說了也徒增煩惱而已\NBesides, it would only bore.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.39,0:56:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要總是取悅別人\NYou don't have to please others all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.43,0:56:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從小的教育就是這樣\NIt's what I've been brought up to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.62,0:56:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想改掉還挺困難的\NDifficult lesson to unlearn.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.03,0:56:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可否發表一個見解?\NWould you permit me an observation?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.81,0:57:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你這麼做是為了讓人們喜歡你\NI believe you do it so that people will love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.78,0:57:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你憑什麼這麼說?      憑我所看到的\NWhat makes you say that?        From what I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.58,0:57:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從你的丈夫 你的朋友 尤其是貝絲夫人\NWith your husband, your friends, especially Lady Bess,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.86,0:57:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是其他公眾\Neven the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.59,0:57:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前還從來沒這麼想過\NI never thought of it that way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.17,0:57:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得我好像很可憐\NYou make me sound so pitiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.24,0:57:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜\NGeorgiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.78,0:57:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過頭了 我向你道歉\NI've gone beyond my brief. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.45,0:57:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請相信我這麼說是為你好\NPlease believe it was only for your sake that I spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.15,0:57:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我到底出什麼事了\NPlease, tell me what is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.96,0:57:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我的一生裏有些事情做得太晚\NI fear I've done some things in life too late
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.90,0:57:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些做得太早\Nand others too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.37,0:58:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你沒有\NNo, you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.56,0:58:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.89,0:59:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.91,0:59:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.58,0:59:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了?\N''All right''?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.49,0:59:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩情相悅嗎?\NDo you love each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.13,0:59:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜      你喜歡貝絲嗎? 大人\NGeorgiana...        Do you love Bess, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.93,0:59:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹什麼?      我對他別無所求\NWhere is all this leading?        I make no demands on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.77,0:59:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲 你喜歡我丈夫嗎?\NAnd, Bess, do you love my husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.64,0:59:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我對你是一樣的\NAs I do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.91,0:59:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你打算留下來?\NAnd so you intend to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.98,0:59:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威廉叫我留下來\NWilliam has asked that I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.49,1:00:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從心底無法拒絕他吧?\NYou couldn't find it in your heart to refuse him?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.89,1:00:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.33,1:00:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們定個協議吧\NThen let us make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.20,1:00:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協議?      是的\NA deal?        Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.67,1:00:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意成全你們\NI give you my blessing
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.98,1:00:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你可以接受我對查爾斯·格雷的感情\Nif you will accept my feelings for Charles Grey.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.38,1:00:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我起初沒有意識到\NI didn't realize it at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.08,1:00:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為那也許只是一種調情\NI thought that perhaps it was only a dalliance.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.09,1:00:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它讓我感到快樂\NIt can make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.80,1:00:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協議? 協議\NA deal? A deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.17,1:00:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不跟人定協議\NI don't make deals.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.07,1:00:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要呢?\NWhy would l?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.04,1:00:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是由我在主宰\NI'm in charge of it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.34,1:00:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以找他出來 我可以挑戰他\NYou know, I would call him out. I would challenge him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.01,1:01:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以一槍打爆他的頭      威廉\NI'd put a bullet in his head.        William.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.75,1:01:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜些\NBe quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.62,1:01:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是決心要讓我淪為大笑柄嗎?\NAre you determined to make me a total laughingstock?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.95,1:01:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個無法生兒子的人 一個戴綠帽的人?\NA man who cannot sire a son, and then a cuckold?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.79,1:01:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威廉 喬治安娜只是說我們...\NWilliam. Georgiana only asks what we ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.06,1:01:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜些! 你這女人!\NBe quiet, woman!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.79,1:01:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是他的婊子嗎?      不是\NAre you his whore?        No.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.63,1:01:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不知道你為什麼要介意\NBut I can't see why you'd mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.90,1:01:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有貝絲 還有三個兒子      三個兒子?\NYou have Bess and three boys!        Three boys?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.51,1:01:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我會讓那些雜種做我的繼承人嗎?\NDo you think I can make those bastards my heirs?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.44,1:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你這樣認為?\NWell? Do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.46,1:01:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威廉!\NWilliam!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.99,1:02:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一點也不瞭解我 是吧?\NYou don't know me in the least, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.09,1:02:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我知道我們是很不合適的一對\NYes, I do. We're a bad match.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.99,1:02:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們結婚時 我要的是兩件事 忠誠和兒子\NI asked but two things when we wed, loyalty and a male heir.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.30,1:02:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你對狗的要求一樣\NThe same as your dogs!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.81,1:02:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 別碰我 別碰我\NNo, don't touch me! Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.85,1:02:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我\NGet off!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.99,1:02:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我\NGet off me!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.89,1:02:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對她也是這樣嗎?你對那個賤人也是這樣嗎?\NIs this how you treat her? Is this how you treat your whore?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.33,1:02:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不!\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.53,1:02:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不! 不!\NNo! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.43,1:02:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不!\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.87,1:03:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來 夏洛特 跟我來\NCome with me. Charlotte, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.64,1:03:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不!\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.87,1:03:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我生個兒子\NGive me a son.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.37,1:03:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 好好呆著 老實聽我的話\NUntil then, stay here and do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.59,1:04:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勝出者是福克斯先生! 人民的選擇!\NI give you the winner. Mr. Fox, the man of the people!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.40,1:04:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請容許我隆重介紹德文郡的公爵夫人\NAnd I give you the weapon, the Duchess of Devonshire.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.29,1:04:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.99,1:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們 謝謝各位參加今天的招待會\NThank you, all of you, for this reception today.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.53,1:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們贏得了選舉 明天我們要構建未來\NToday we have won the vote. Tomorrow we define the future!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.18,1:04:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵     公爵\NYour Grace.        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.69,1:04:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵      公爵\NYour Grace.        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.26,1:05:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵\NYour Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.66,1:05:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵      公爵\NYour Grace.        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.79,1:05:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵夫人 能否請您跳支舞?\NWill Your Grace give me the favor of a dance?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.48,1:06:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站穩點 喬\NSteady, G.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.62,1:06:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,著火了!      喬治安娜!\NFire!        Georgiana!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.22,1:06:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人!\NYour Grace!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.76,1:06:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人的頭髮!\NHer Grace's hair!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.23,1:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想辦法啊!\NDo something!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.34,1:06:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夫人頭髮上的火滅掉\NPlease put out Her Grace's hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.48,1:07:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人需要休息\NHer Grace needs to rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.62,1:07:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要她謹遵醫囑\NAs long as she follows strict instructions
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.78,1:07:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生產就不應該會有問題\Nthere should be no impediment to the birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.85,1:07:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.89,1:07:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵夫人有孕了\NThe Duchess is pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.40,1:07:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德文郡\NDevonshire
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.26,1:07:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這裏\NAnd there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.96,1:07:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 希頓\NThank you, Heaton.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.50,1:08:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來\NCome.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.88,1:08:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人\NYour Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.88,1:08:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照公爵大人的繼承權條約 這是給你的\NAs per the terms of His Grace's inheritance, this is for you
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.49,1:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任你支配\Nto spend as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.96,1:08:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於成功了\NSuccess at last.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.31,1:08:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜\NGeorgiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.91,1:08:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對此也深感痛恨\NI, too, abhor this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.40,1:09:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換還是不換?\NTwist or stick?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.37,1:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不換      不換?\NStick.        Stick?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.64,1:09:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不換了\NI'll stick, too, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.38,1:09:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻開看看\NLet's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.61,1:09:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你贏了 真厲害\NYou won. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.46,1:09:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你忘了發牌了\NMama, you forgot to deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.02,1:09:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人      格雷先生\NYour Grace.        Mr. Grey.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.55,1:10:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從法國被召回了?      暫時的\NYou are recalled from France?        For a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.72,1:10:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有革命嗎?\NNo revolution yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.83,1:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有 不過是遲早的事\NNo, not yet, but it's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.37,1:10:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會來這裏?      我接到一個請柬\NHow is it you are here?        I received an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.31,1:10:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為那是黨派的邀請 不能拒絕\NI assumed it was on behalf of the Party. I could not say no.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.58,1:10:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.25,1:10:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我生了個兒子\NI bore a son.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.52,1:10:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.96,1:10:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫威廉·喬治·斯賓塞·卡文迪什\NHis name is William George Spencer Cavendish,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.52,1:10:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈廷頓侯爵\NMarquis of Hartington.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.72,1:10:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們叫他哈特\NWe call him Hart.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.43,1:10:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和公爵一定都很高興吧\NYou and the Duke must be very pleased.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.80,1:10:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NWe are.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.04,1:10:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公爵到倫敦慶祝去了\NThe Duke has gone to London to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.85,1:11:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你\NYou have been missed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.56,1:11:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很想你\NMuch missed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.23,1:11:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Q押5\NQueen on five.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.47,1:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請停止下注\NAnd no more bets, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.44,1:11:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輸牌是 4\NThe losing card, four.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.61,1:11:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贏牌是 Q\NThe winning card, Queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.64,1:12:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好極了 八押3\NJolly good. Eight on the three.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.14,1:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在5上押五\NPut five on the five.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.98,1:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5都已經沒了 喬\NAll of the fives have gone, G.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.52,1:12:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我累得不想再玩了\NI think I'm too tired to play.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.79,1:12:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生們 失陪了     夫人\NGentlemen.        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.00,1:12:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜\NGeorgiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.24,1:12:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可讓任何人知道\NNo one must know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.31,1:12:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你召回格雷的?     晚安\NYou summoned Grey.        Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.03,1:14:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算去巴斯\NI was thinking about going to Bath.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.61,1:15:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲 我去休養時\NBess, you can stay here
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.54,1:15:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以留下來照顧我們的丈夫\Nand look after our husband whilst I take the cure.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.92,1:15:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 威廉 為什麼不呢?\NYes, William. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.39,1:15:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她現在去了 在你有空時我們可以去找她\NIf G goes now, we can catch up with her when you're free.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.19,1:15:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 如果你一定要去\NWell, if you must.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.97,1:15:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"德文郡的公爵夫人"\N"The Duchess of Devonshire "
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.17,1:15:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"上周戴著室內帽出現在巴斯"\N"appeared last week in Bath in a mobcap."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.22,1:15:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"自從公爵夫人"\N"Her Grace,"
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.51,1:15:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"被邀請參與選舉活動以來"\Never since initiation into the business of electioneering,"
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.48,1:15:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"她就跟公眾走得很近"\N"has been much attached to the mobs."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.64,1:15:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好\NVery good.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.79,1:15:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜歡哪一個\NSo which one is your favorite?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.23,1:15:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一個      是呀\NThis one.        Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.66,1:15:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張好像是你難得一次連贏幾把\NIn this one it seems you've hit a winning streak, for once.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.95,1:16:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好\NVery good.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.17,1:16:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這一張...\NAnd in this one you see...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.81,1:16:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿這身衣服去吸引投票者合適嗎?\NIs that dress really an appropriate way to attract voters?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.71,1:16:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們政治家對服裝真是一無所知\NYou politicians know absolutely nothing about fashion.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.65,1:16:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的問我最喜歡哪一個\NBut if you were to really ask me which my favorite was,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.89,1:16:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會說是這一個\NI'd say it was this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.47,1:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 查爾斯      早上好\NMorning, Charles.        Morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.67,1:16:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 先生\NGood day to you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.77,1:17:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好 謝謝\NIt's perfect. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.96,1:17:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為會給你一個驚喜呢 喬\NThought we would surprise you, G.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.46,1:17:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你說過我們的婚姻生活裏\NI think you once said there wasn't enough spontaneity
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.33,1:17:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欠缺一些主動\Nin our marriage
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.52,1:17:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是類似的話\Nor words to that effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.91,1:17:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親 你怎麼會來這裏\NMama, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.78,1:17:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你見過我們在巴斯的一些朋友嗎?\NSo, have you seen many of our circle in Bath?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.92,1:17:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見過一些\NSome.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.35,1:18:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科克斯一家還有哈弗福德和威克洛男爵\NThe Cokes and Haverford and Lord Wicklow.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.79,1:18:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一些政治家是吧 一些會議什麼的\NBunch of politicos, too, aren't there? Meetings and such.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.33,1:18:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是吧\NI believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.43,1:18:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格雷在這裏嗎? 我是說查爾斯·格雷\NIs Grey here? By which I mean Mr. Charles Grey.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.80,1:18:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有傳聞說他在這裏\NRumor has it that he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.04,1:18:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄他的     喬治安娜\NI won't give him up.        Georgiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.87,1:18:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有一個心愛的人 貝絲是我丈夫的愛人\NEveryone has a lover. Bess is the lover of my husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.14,1:18:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有任何的判斷能力\NIf you had shown some discretion,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.91,1:18:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情可能會更得很不同     很不同?\Nit might have been different.        Different?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.41,1:18:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一幸運的是這一切還沒上過報紙\NThe only good fortune is it hasn't yet made it to the papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.95,1:18:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 格雷獨身 他沒有財產 沒有官爵\NMy dear, Grey is unmarried. He has no wealth, no rank.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.89,1:18:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事他無需擔任何風險 你將承受所有傷害\NHe risks nothing with this affair. The hazard is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.42,1:18:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格雷是愛我的     威廉也一樣\NGrey loves me.        So does William.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.36,1:18:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我愛你\NYes. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.40,1:18:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼愛?\NHow?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.43,1:18:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我所理解的愛的方式\NIn the way I understand love.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.07,1:18:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜 這事做得太過頭了\NGeorgiana, this has gone much too far.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.46,1:18:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有失我們的身份\NIt is beneath our dignity.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.87,1:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個倫敦都在談論     讓他們說吧\NAll London is talking.        Let them talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.35,1:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果格雷令我淪為墮落的女人 我不介意\NIf Grey makes me a fallen woman, well and good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.98,1:19:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威廉可以跟我離婚\NNow William may divorce me
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.21,1:19:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓貝絲成為德文郡公爵夫人\Nand Bess becomes Duchess of Devonshire.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.66,1:19:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的\NThat will never happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.66,1:19:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了\NI think I will leave you to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.53,1:19:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在要怎麼樣呢\NWhat follows now?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.83,1:19:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要撕開我的衣服\NAre you going to tear my clothes off
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.26,1:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次對我用強嗎?\Nand force yourself upon me again?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.20,1:19:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要這麼做?\NWhy on earth would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.31,1:19:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你從未思考過\NI know that you've never thought much of
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.08,1:19:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的才智和行事方式 喬\Nmy manners or my intellect, G.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.65,1:19:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事實上 我從不做沒用的事\NBut, in fact, I never do anything that serves no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.92,1:19:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全清楚你們為什麼在一起\NI know precisely what you two have together.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.89,1:19:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們彼此相愛     我毫不懷疑\NWe love each other.        I do not doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.82,1:19:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟你一樣是個理想主義者\NHe is a dreamer like yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.62,1:19:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們都在夢想一個\Nand you both dream of another world
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.20,1:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不曾也將不會存在的世界\Nthat does not exist and it never will.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.33,1:19:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在現實中呢 讓我給你點啟示\NAs for reality, allow me to enlighten you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.17,1:19:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不立即與他斷絕關係\NIf you do not give him up at once,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.21,1:19:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會調查整個國家\NI will see to it that every home
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.98,1:20:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與他關聯所有家庭和賬本\Nand every checkbook in this country is closed to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.64,1:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他將會為所有的政府部門\NHe will be welcomed neither in the halls of government
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.58,1:20:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和權力機構所拒絕\Nnor in its backrooms of power.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.28,1:20:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想成為首相的夢想\NHis dream of becoming prime minister
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.22,1:20:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你們想要改變世界的幻想都將化為灰燼\Nand your mutual fantasy of a changed world will be dead as ash.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.53,1:20:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你也將永遠看不到你的孩子\NAnd you will never see your children again.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.91,1:20:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜\NGeorgiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.62,1:21:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要請你回倫敦去\NI must ask you to return to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.06,1:21:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不去?     是的\NWithout you?        Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.53,1:21:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的女兒讓我帶的\NThese are from our girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.04,1:21:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小哈特沒有寫\NLittle Hart neglected to write,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.45,1:21:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他太小也寫不了\Nbut then, of course, he's not yet one.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.82,1:21:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這將是你一生中最大的錯誤     不\NThis will be the mistake of your life.        No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.29,1:21:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多年前我已經犯過那個錯了\NI made that many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.50,1:22:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你自己可以離開吧\NI trust you can see yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.25,1:22:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死的 打門打開       是的 大人\NDamn you, man, open the door!        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.47,1:24:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽 媽媽 媽媽\NMama, Mama, Mama, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.05,1:24:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽 媽媽\NMama, Mama, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.33,1:24:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 孩子們     媽媽 我愛你\NCome on, girls.        Mama. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.77,1:25:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們 去吧 媽媽一會兒就來\NGirls, run along. Your mother will join you in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.67,1:25:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.05,1:25:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\NRun along.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.82,1:25:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬\NG.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.13,1:25:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我很高興\NYou must know how greatly pleased I am
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.00,1:25:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於能夠達成妥協\Nthat we have come to an arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.14,1:25:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓孩子們離開母親太久\NIt's not good for little ones to
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.39,1:25:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是件好事\Nbe without their mother for so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.34,1:25:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生是為了他們     這是一種理解方式\NMy life for theirs.        That's one way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.68,1:25:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你母親稱之為\NYour mother called it
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.32,1:25:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"眾人尊嚴高於個人欲求"\N"common decency before personal gratification,"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.94,1:25:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是類似的話 具體我不記得\Nor some such thing. The exact words escape me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.76,1:25:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說"被囚困在自己的家中"\NHow about "imprisoned in my own house"?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.16,1:25:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 她不是這麼說的\NNo. That's not how she put it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.77,1:26:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則我會記得\NI would have remembered that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.53,1:26:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜!\NGeorgiana!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.26,1:26:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!\NUnhand me!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.20,1:26:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜!\NGeorgiana!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.27,1:26:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜! 請放開我!\NGeorgiana! Will you please unhand me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.24,1:26:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.75,1:26:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜! 放開\NGeorgiana! Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.02,1:26:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜!\NGeorgiana!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.92,1:26:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 伯利     放開他\NThank you, Burleigh.        Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.23,1:27:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每天寄出十幾封信\NI have written a dozen times a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.46,1:27:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可沒有你的任何回音\NStill, there is nothing from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.03,1:27:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事? 你不再愛我了嗎?\NWhat has happened? Do you love me no longer?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.04,1:27:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的個人感覺從未改變\NMy personal feelings remain unaltered.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.02,1:27:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就應該在一起\NThen we must be together again.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.58,1:27:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想娶你 我想與你生兒育女\NI want to marry you. I want you to bear my children.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.28,1:27:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我才不在乎是男孩還是女孩!\NAnd I don't care if they're boys or girls!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.26,1:27:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望能夠這樣    可以的 會的\NI wish it could be that way.        It can. It will.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.72,1:27:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論我們如何躲避 悲傷總是難免的\NSorrows will come however we try to avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.85,1:27:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須堅持到底 永不放棄\NWe must stay the course and never give in.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.19,1:27:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 查爾斯      你必須要跟我離開\NNo, Charles.        You must leave and be with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.06,1:27:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做一個自由的女人 走吧 我們現在就走\NA free woman. Now! Let us leave now!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.33,1:27:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能丟下我的孩子\NI cannot abandon my children.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.33,1:27:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想你要我做的是什麼吧\NListen to what you are asking me to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.19,1:28:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 不喜歡吃鴿子嗎?\NWhat's the matter? Don't like the pigeon?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.06,1:28:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得挺好吃的\NI find it quite decent.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.61,1:28:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懷了查爾斯·格雷的孩子\NI'm carrying Charles Grey's child.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.59,1:29:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我向公爵夫人轉達我的決定\NPlease be so kind as to inform the Duchess of my decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.23,1:29:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情的安排是這樣的\NThis is how it will be.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.56,1:29:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會被送到鄉下\NYou will be taken to the country
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.80,1:29:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把孩子生下來\Nwhere you will give birth to the child,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.73,1:29:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子將會由查爾斯·格雷的家庭\Nand the child will be trusted to the care
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.44,1:29:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撫養成人\Nof Charles Grey's family.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.84,1:29:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽嗎?\NAre you listening?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.51,1:29:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她聽到了 我們走吧\NI think she's heard you. Let's leave her.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.61,1:29:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治安娜 拜託     我說我們走了\NGeorgiana, please.        I said let's leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.75,1:29:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是在討論問題 她已經聽到我的決定了\NThis is not a discussion. She's been informed of my decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.25,1:29:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對她有點同情心吧 威廉     同情什麼\NHave pity on her, William.        Pity be damned.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.32,1:29:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是她自找的 你是清楚的\NShe's brought this upon herself, as well you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.76,1:29:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧      不 我要跟她去\NNow come.        No. I will go with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.86,1:29:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你哪裏也不許去\NBut you're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.53,1:29:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟她去 如果她願意的話\NI will go with G, if G will have me,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.33,1:29:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論你做什麼說什麼都阻止不了我們\Nand there's nothing you can do or say to stop either of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.59,1:30:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你來陪我     我不可以讓你單獨一人\NThank you for coming.        I couldn't not be with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.76,1:31:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該走了\NIt's time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.43,1:31:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要讓...      不 我要自己去\NWould it help...        No, I must take her.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.49,1:33:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人  我是格雷將軍\NYour Grace, I'm General Grey.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.66,1:33:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查爾斯呢?\NWhere's Charles?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.13,1:33:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫說最好由我來處理這件事\NYour husband thought it best if I took care of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.17,1:33:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格雷將軍\NGeneral Grey.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.37,1:33:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字叫伊萊扎\NHer name is Eliza.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.05,1:34:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.80,1:34:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  喬 都過去了 都過去了\NCome on, G. I've got you. I've got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.42,1:35:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很擅於表達自己\NI'm not particularly adept at expressing myself
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.09,1:36:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是在牽涉到個人情感時\Nwhen it comes to matters of a more personal nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.70,1:36:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想試一下\NBut I shall try.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.31,1:36:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這幾年來 我的所作所為\NOver the years, I have acted in ways
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.28,1:36:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你看來很無情\Nthat you have judged to be harsh.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.62,1:36:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你再受任何折磨了\NWell, I do not wish for you to undergo any further suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.06,1:36:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上 我希望我們能擁有平靜的生活\NIn fact, I would like our lives to find a calm normality.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.00,1:36:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾本夫人安排了一次聚會\NLady Melbourne has arranged a small gathering
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.37,1:36:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慶祝你度假歸來\Nin honor of your recent return from holiday.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.74,1:36:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基於這幾年來\NAnd given some of the vague reports
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.16,1:36:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流傳的一些流言蜚語\Nthat have been circulating this past year
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.50,1:36:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們最好能出席\NI think it would be wise for us to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.99,1:36:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是表現一下和睦\NA show of unity, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.06,1:37:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰會去?\NWho will be there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.00,1:37:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人\NEverybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.47,1:37:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如你所願吧\NAs you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.42,1:38:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此自由自在是多麼美好呀\NHow wonderful to be that free.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.12,1:38:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 喬喬 來啊\NCome here. Little G, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.83,1:38:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德文郡公爵和公爵夫人\NThe Duke and Duchess of Devonshire
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.92,1:38:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有伊麗莎白·福斯特夫人\Nand Lady Elizabeth Foster.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.02,1:39:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人      見到你真高興\NYour Grace.        It's lovely to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.45,1:39:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 夫人\NWelcome back, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.86,1:39:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.03,1:39:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來      歡迎回來 夫人\NWelcome back.        Welcome home, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.40,1:39:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來      歡迎回來 喬\NWelcome back.        Welcome back, G.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.40,1:39:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一直都非常地想念您\NYour presence has been sorely missed.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.94,1:40:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下\NWould you excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.21,1:40:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格雷先生      夫人\NMr. Grey.        Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.09,1:40:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你們的旅程一定很愉快吧\NI trust your tour was enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.96,1:40:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.59,1:40:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在瑞士過的夏天 在尼斯過的冬天\NWe spent the summer in Switzerland and the winter in Nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.56,1:40:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我代表各位賓客\NWell, I speak on behalf of everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.77,1:40:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你的安全歸來表示由衷的高興\Nwhen I say how glad I am that you have arrived home safely.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.04,1:40:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近可好?\NAnd what news with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.55,1:40:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要訂婚了\NI'm to be engaged.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.15,1:40:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟潘森比小姐\NTo Lady Ponsonby.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.72,1:40:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會向大家宣佈的\NThe announcement will follow shortly.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.92,1:40:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你\NCongratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.00,1:41:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有了一個侄女 叫伊萊扎\NAnd I have a niece, Eliza,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.10,1:41:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都很寵愛她\Nwho is very much loved.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.41,1:41:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改天你得來見見她\NOne day you should come and meet her,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.15,1:41:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久以後\Nin a little while.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.95,1:41:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你願意的話\NIf you would like.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.59,1:41:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常願意\NI would like that very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.13,1:41:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治亞娜重返社交界
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.60,1:41:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續成為當代最富盛名
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.60,1:41:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最具影響力的女人
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.89,1:42:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查爾斯·格雷成為英國首相
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.96,1:42:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治亞娜 貝絲還有公爵一直生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.79,1:42:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到喬治亞娜去世
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.59,1:42:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在喬治亞娜的祝福下
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.90,1:42:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲嫁給了公爵
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.89,1:42:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為下一任公爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.08,1:42:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看誰先抓到我\NWho's going to catch me first?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.52,1:43:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我!      快 孩子們\NMe!        Quick, girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.15,1:43:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 我要跑掉啦\NQuick, I'm going to get away!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.22,1:43:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 孩子們 追上我\NCome on, girls, keep running.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.62,1:43:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治亞娜經常秘密探訪伊萊扎
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.64,1:43:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你\NAnd I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.63,1:43:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊萊扎將她的女兒命名為喬治亞娜


